== 经济 ==
2009年，全县完成生产总值35.4亿元，实现财政总收入3.66亿元。<ref>{{cite web|title=县情简介|url=http://www.yymhw.com/a/20100225/1267089734.html|publisher=弋阳门户网|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111123014718/http://www.yymhw.com/a/20100225/1267089734.html|archivedate=2011-11-23}}</ref>

